questions.transcript: What was your experience like with vaccination?

perspective_statements.transcript: I appreciate hearing your perspective on it.
I really enjoyed learning more about your own experiences.

general_notes: The participant AEF1C is skeptical of the vaccine due to the history of the healthcare industry. He is also very confident in his own health and therefore does not feel the need to get vaccinated. He is respectful of others' decisions to get vaccinated.
